title: Djet Donald La'ala
text: Jet Donald La'ala is an Indonesian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who played for <a href="Indonesia%20national%20football%20team">Indonesia</a> in the <a href="2000%20Asian%20Cup">2000 Asian Cup</a>. He also played for <a href="Palu%20Putra">Palu Putra</a>, <a href="Pupuk%20Kaltim%20Bontang">Pupuk Kaltim Bontang</a>, <a href="PSM%20Makassar">PSM Makassar</a>, <a href="Persija%20Jakarta">Persija Jakarta</a>, <a href="Persmin%20Minahasa">Persmin Minahasa</a>, <a href="Pesma%20Manado">Pesma Manado</a>.
